<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-sky-500">Portfolio</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl text-pretty sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
        How our platform has evolved
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
        A timeline of the systems, features, and engineering milestones that shaped Business OS — the core engine powering our Clinic and Commercial Platforms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white pb-24 sm:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <ol class="relative border-l border-gray-200 space-y-16">

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">1</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">April 2020 — Initial Platform Architecture</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Launched the foundation of our multi‑tenant Business OS using Rails 8, Turbo, and Postgres.  
            Introduced accounts, users, permissions, and secure onboarding — the backbone of all future platforms.
          </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">2</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2021 — Instant Website Builder</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Built a dynamic website generator with templates, forms, submissions, and analytics.  
            Enabled clinics and commercial businesses to launch branded, conversion‑ready sites in minutes.
          </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">3</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2022 — OAuth Identity Suite</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Integrated Apple, Google, Microsoft, LinkedIn, Facebook, and GitHub OAuth.  
            Delivered secure authentication and brand‑accurate UI for all platforms.
          </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">4</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2023 — Developer Command Center</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Released a polished dashboard for developers to manage accounts, users, websites, and submissions.  
            Added animations, improved UX, and Tailwind v4 enhancements.
          </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">5</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2024 — Business Operations Suite</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Introduced calendars, bookings, staff roles, payments, customer portals, and real‑time notifications.  
            Formed the operational core for both Clinic Platform and Commercial Platform.
          </p>
        </li>

        <!-- Milestone -->
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-white">6</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2025 — Bilingual Platform (EN/ES)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-base/7">
            Added full English and Spanish support across Business OS.  
            Empowered clinics and commercial teams to serve diverse staff and clients across regions.
          </p>
        </li>

      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
