        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Launch branded websites with forms, submissions, and analytics in minutes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">OAuth Identity Suite</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
