          A command center for managing accounts, users, websites, and submissions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Business Operations Suite</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Calendars, bookings, payments, staff roles, customer portals, and more.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Analytics & Automations</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          Real‑time insights and automated workflows that keep businesses moving.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
